Text: "My travel story is going to be excited and full of interesting events as any\
  \ previous adventures for me, traveling to Argentina will feeds my soul beauty and\
  \ purifies my heart from the difficult events and the problems that happened to\
  \ me during my life. Argentina is one of the heavens on earth that\u2019s what I\
  \ heard from my dad after his visit to this beautiful country, I wish I can go visit\
  \ this earth\u2019s heaven with just my notebook and pencil. As I\u2019m still a\
  \ student I wish winning this trip to till my dear friends about the events and\
  \ to enlighten them about this this beautiful country Argentina."
